## Limitations

The report is based on available online sources, which may not cover all aspects of the complex motivations behind the 9/11 attacks. Some sources may contain biases or lack comprehensive details. Additionally, the analysis is limited to the information available up to October 2023, and new insights or declassified information may alter the understanding of the events and motivations behind the attacks.